    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A computer interface that behaves as both an input and output device. The surface of the monitor screen is overlaid with sensors of various types that allow the user to trigger software tasks.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
